data.name: description2.Text
data.value: Let your romance blossom like never before - gorgeous red roses and carnations, ornately decorated with sprays of white statice, all tied together with gorgeous hues of gold and black. Our Mirabella flower bouquet is the perfect way to add a touch of magic on just about any day!

data.name: Label9.Text
data.value: Indulge in the enchantment of life's treasured moments with Enchanted Bloom's exquisite rose bouquet. Meticulously handcrafted from the finest blossoms, immerse yourself in a world of elegance and beauty. Don't wait, seize the moment and order now to experience our seamless same-day delivery service across the nation.

data.name: description.Text
data.value: Red roses complimented by fine Baby Breaths (Gypsophila) makes this bouquet an absolute stunner! Elegantly wrapped, this bouquet is perfect for romantic occasions, birthdays or anniversaries as it represents your love and tenderness well. A bouquet that speaks for you!

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: No one should have a blue Christmas this holiday season! - Charm the heart of your special someone with a flower arrangement decked with the most dashing red roses, white poing pongs and pine cone ornaments; accompanied with eucalyptus baby blue, baby breath and yellow tea leaves.With such a beautiful flower gift, it will take anyone's breath away! Especially Under The Mistletoe.

data.name: description4.Text
data.value: The Sweetheart Bouquet impresses with lush red roses, fine baby breath and white lilies. Sure to please that someone special this combination of premium flowers comes with lavish wrapping and a nice ribbon.
